<subSubSection pageId="22" pageNumber="101" type="dispersal potential">
<paragraph pageId="22" pageNumber="101">Dispersal potential.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="22" pageNumber="101">These beetles are macropterous and capable of flight. They are moderately swift and agile runners.</paragraph>
